snippet.title: Amber Heard’s Friends Reveal They Think Amber Heard Will End Up in Prison
snippet.description:
You’ve probably heard about the legal battle between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, but while many celebrities and fans are siding with Depp, you probably didn’t know that even Amber Heard’s friends are against her! Find out why they think she’ll end up in prison on What’s Poppin!

Find out more about their legal battle here: https://youtu.be/3DrcP0z7Mus
